  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Type 2 diabetes mellitus with HbA1c 6.5-9%, fasting glucose of 126-200 mg/dl and BMI
             of 27-40.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient treated with insulin, GLP-1 analog or weight reduction medications.

          -  Type 1 diabetes

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Renal failure (creatinin &gt;1.4 for male and 1.3 for female

          -  Uncontrolled hypertension (&gt;160/100)

          -  Abnormal thyroid function test

          -  Patient treated with steroids or psychiatric medications.
      </textblock>
